{"tid":2458457,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"觀察員A 就魚丸一事致歉: 係啦 !! 係啦 !! 我地波台唔岩啦!! 梳鳩 ry 囉,得未呀,好未呀 !!!!!!!","createTime":"2021-03-23T12:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T05:26:02.000Z","uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a5357ba93795b603ca5b31b7fe1cf3e25b27ab40","tid":2458457,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>港超聯 愉園就「女球證」事件致歉</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20210322/photo/bkn-20210322192740773-0322_00882_001_01p.jpg?20210322195116\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20210322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210322192740773-0322_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20210322195116&h=248e62da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">Admin: 叫咗你啲標題咪咁撚誇鳩張架啦, 出事架嘛</span><br />\n<br />\n周日（21日）天水圍飛馬對愉園的賽事，愉園主教練鮑家耀賽後批評主裁判羅碧芝的言論，惹來輿論的抨擊，更被指涉及性別歧視。愉園會方一天後（22日）於Facebook發聲明，承認「鮑Sir」的言論不恰當，並向有關人士及外界致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_Ocszs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_Ocszs_1200x0.png&h=9efd4d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">觀察員A: 係啦, 係啦, 我唔岩啦, 得未呀 !!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n愉園在周日（21日）的港超聯賽事，以0比1不敵天水圍飛馬。賽事中擔任主裁判員的國際女球證羅碧芝，賽後被愉園主帥鮑家耀批評判決錯漏百出，要求足總不應再派女性球證擔任男子賽事的裁判員，言論被外界指牽涉性別歧視。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/football_hkpl_pegasus_happyvalley_20210321-23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2Ffootball_hkpl_pegasus_happyvalley_20210321-23.jpg&h=20bf0867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">N賓: 今晚排長龍呀, 走啦 on9 仔</span><br />\n<br />\n事件發酵一天，愉園會方周一（22日）在Facebook發聲明，稱球會領導層與鮑經過討論後，皆承認有關言論措辭不恰當，即使有關言論僅為回應裁判當日的執法表現，並非針對個別群體，亦屬不必要。<br />\n聲明又提到，「快活谷」領導層及主教練鮑家耀，就事件向受有關人士及外界致歉，並會認真反省，避免同類事件再次發生。而球隊亦會在近期召開隊內座談會，提醒職、球員謹言慎行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/football_hkpl_pegasus_happyvalley_20210321-17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2Ffootball_hkpl_pegasus_happyvalley_20210321-17.jpg&h=9d783a58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">佩主席: 嘩屌, 濕晒吖喂 !!</span>"},{"pid":"6dfc8b6d1e1a78148ecb179a61d55b0e09681fa5","tid":2458457,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd54d30d15ebda743aa87e4328549098737d981","tid":2458457,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:28:17.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3a72bc57382f87a9c06d00cd74564bd47e3ed1","tid":2458457,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"我都要向羅小姐致歉。"},{"pid":"8f6ae2637b2d630097846fd5afd25ed52a36d53c","tid":2458457,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa3a72bc57382f87a9c06d00cd74564bd47e3ed1","tid":2458457,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"我都要向羅小姐致歉。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"你唔好再搞事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}